stems%20that%20generate%20and%20distribute%20power%20close%20to%20the%20point%20of%20consumption%2C%20rather%20than%20depending%20on%20a%20central%20grid.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20every%20rural%20household%20in%20the%20country%20would%20be%20familiar%20with%20a%20solar%20panel%20for%20mobile%20charging%2C%20or%20a%20solar%20lantern%2C%20they%20might%20not%20imagine%20that%20solar%20could%20be%20used%20to%20grow%20fodder%20or%20as%20a%20cold%20storage%20solution.%20So%20the%20awareness%20gap%20is%20pretty%20big.%20Until%20they%20actually%20see%20it%20in%20action%2C%20it%20might%20prove%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20decide%20to%20buy%20it.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20Powering%20Livelihoods%20programme%20comes%20in%3B%20we%20invite%20them%20to%20witness%20successful%20models.%20These%20demo%20champions%20%E2%80%94%20early%20adopters%20of%20the%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20then%20demonstrate%20the%20technology%20to%20others%20in%20their%20area.%20Speaking%20to%20existing%20users%20gives%20them%20perspective%20and%20builds%20their%20confidence.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaveen%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20seeking%20out%20a%20solar-powered%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakki%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20gauged%20the%20pulse%20of%20the%20market%20by%20speaking%20to%20other%20micro-preneurs%20who%E2%80%99d%20taken%20the%20leap%20from%20diesel%20to%20solar.%20He%20judges%20success%20by%20certain%20fundamental%20yardsticks%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoes%20it%20work%20well%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20efficiency%20like%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20happy%20with%20your%20decision%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20confidence%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282854%2Fmaharashtra-family-solar-drying-machine-food-processing-chikoo-increases-sales