20among%20apps%2C%20so%20this%20will%20only%20impact%20a%20small%20number%20of%20users%2C%20but%20it's%20important%20to%20be%20aware%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMinor%20drawbacks%20aside%2C%20the%20Acer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20is%20easily%20one%20of%20the%20best%20student%20laptops%20for%20most%20needs.%20It's%20quick%2C%20lasts%20all%20day%2C%20and%20won't%20strain%20your%20back%20carrying%20it.%20%3Cspan%3EThat's%20all%20worthy%20of%20a%20hearty%20recommendation%20from%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Facer-swift-go-14-ai-laptop-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAcer%20Swift%20Go%2014%20AI%20laptop%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22217c3c3a-8b7d-4be3-9427-c000ba4a399d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20MacBook%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20MacBook%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWalk%20into%20any%20university%20lecture%20hall%2C%20and%20you'll%20be%20greeted%20by%20a%20sea%20of%20Apple%20logos.%20The%202025%2013-inch%20MacBook%20Air%20is%20a%20great%20example%20of%20what%20makes%20Macs%20so%20popular%3A%20It%20looks%20and%20performs%20great%2C%20it's%20simple%20to%20use%2C%20and%20it%20gains%20extra%20features%20when%20run%20alongside%20other%20Apple%20devices%20like%20an%20iPhone%20or%20iPad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20every%20MacBook%20looks%20the%20same%20on%20the%20outside.%20But%20the%20MacBook%20Air%20gets%20its%20name%20from%20its%20thin%20frame%3A%20It's%20a%20bit%20smaller%20across%20all%20dimensions%20than%20the%20MacBook%20Pro%2C%20and%20nearly%20a%20pound%20lighter.%20This%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20carry%20around%20campus%20either%20in%20your%20arms%20or%20in%20a%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20smaller%20footprint%20does%20require%20some%20sacrifices%2C%20but%20they're%20minor.%20The%20MacBook%20Air's%20battery%20is%20smaller%20than%20the%20Pro's%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20but%20you%20should%20still%20expect%20about%2010%20hours%20or%20more%20on%20a%20single%20charge.%20The%20Air%20also%20lacks%20an%20HDMI%20port%20and%20SD%20card%20reader%2C%20but%20you%20can%20add%20those%20using%20external%20USB%20dongles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20although%20the%20screen%20is%20the%20smallest%20on%20any%20current-gen%20MacBook%2C%20it's%20still%20better%20than%20almost%20any%20other%20laptop%20display%2C%20maxing%20out%20at%20a%20bright%20500%20nits%20with%20vibrant%20color%20support%20and%20a%20QHD%202560x1664%20resolution.%20Apple%20knows%20how%20to%20design%20screens%2C%20and%20that's%20on%20full%20display%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%202015%2013-inch%20MacBook%20Air%20resting%20on%20a%20table%20in%20a%20garden.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b0a1f3cfc04e97619c3b68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%202025%20MacBook%20Air%20is%20the%20best%20value%20overall%20in%20Apple's%20current%20laptop%20lineup.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Antonelli%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20laptop's%20size%20doesn't%20kill%20its%20power%2C%20either.%20It%20boasts%20an%20M4%20chip%2C%20one%20of%20the%20newest%20in%20the%20brand's%20exclusive%20%26quot%3BApple%20Silicon%26quot%3B%20line.%20It's%20not%20as%20beefy%20as%20the%20M4%20Pro%20or%20Max%20chips%20you'll%20find%20in%20a%20MacBook%20Pro%2C%20but%20it's%20fast%20enough%20to%20run%20nearly%20any%20program%20you%20want%2C%20from%20your%20standard%20internet%20browser%20to%20content%20creation%20apps%20like%20Final%20Cut%20Pro.%20Geekbench%20tests%20give%20it%20an%20average%20CPU%20score%20of%2014%2C862.%20That%20puts%20it%20on%20par%20with%20the%20best%2013th-gen%20Intel%20CPUs%2C%20and%20it's%20even%20better%20than%20the%20CPU%20on%20my%20high-end%20Windows%20pick%20in%20this%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20top%20Windows%20laptops%20trounce%20the%20MacBook%20Air%20on%20the%20graphics%20front.%20MacBooks%20have%20never%20been%20known%20for%20their%20graphical%20performance%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20gaming.%20And%20although%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-use-macbook-for-gaming%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egaming%20on%20macOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20better%20now%20than%20it's%20ever%20been%2C%20it's%20still%20not%20the%20operating%20system%20of%20choice%20if%20you%20want%20to%20play%20the%20biggest%2C%20newest%20games%20on%20release%20day.%20Geekbench%20testing%20gives%20it%20an%20average%20GPU%20score%20of%2035%2C734%2C%20which%20is%20about%20on%20par%20with%20a%202016%2010-series%20Nvidia%20GeForce%20graphics%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20lack%20of%20graphical%20power%20is%20one%20of%20macOS'%20many%20quirks%2C%20which%20can%20be%20awkward%20for%20native%20Windows%20or%20ChromeOS%20users%20to%20get%20used%20to.%20Compared%20to%20Windows%20laptops%2C%20MacBooks%20are%20restrictive.%20They're%20not%20as%20customizable%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20hardware%20and%20settings.%20Not%20all%20Windows%20apps%20work%20on%20macOS%2C%20and%20vice%20versa.%20And%20they're%20also%20much%20harder%20to%20repair%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20costly%20problem.%20MacBooks%20are%20built%20for%20users%20who%20want%20a%20laptop%20that'll%20just%20%3Cem%3Ework%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20without%20any%20need%20to%20fiddle%20with%20the%20settings.%20Some%20students%20will%20find%20that%20a%20relief%2C%20while%20others%20will%20want%20more%20control%20over%20their%20laptop%20experience.%20Your%20mileage%20may%20vary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20the%20biggest%20downside%20to%20buying%20a%20MacBook%20was%20the%20price%2C%20which%20was%20often%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20higher%20than%20comparable%20PCs.%20These%20days%2C%20with%20chip%20shortages%20and%20tariffs%20raising%20costs%20across%20other%20brands%20in%20the%20laptop%20market%2C%20MacBooks%20are%20actually%20much%20more%20competitively%20priced.%20The%20configurati