%20a%20bit%20like%20your%20laptop's%20short-term%20memory.%20It%20keeps%20track%20of%20which%20programs%20you%20have%20running%20and%20what%20they're%20displaying%2C%20so%20when%20you%20click%20on%20their%20window%20again%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20they'll%20respond%20immediately.%20It%20works%20the%20same%20way%20with%20browser%20tabs%2C%20which%20rely%20on%20RAM%20to%20let%20you%20switch%20between%20them%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERAM%20tends%20to%20come%20in%20three%20different%20amounts%3A%208GB%2C%2016GB%2C%20and%2032GB.%20The%20more%20RAM%20you%20have%2C%20the%20faster%20you%20can%20multitask.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20student%20will%20be%20just%20fine%20with%2016GB%20of%20RAM.%20That's%20enough%20to%20run%20a%20few%20apps%20at%20a%20time%20and%20handle%20some%20heavy%20tab%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202025%2C%208GB%20simply%20isn't%20enough%20to%20handle%20modern%20applications%20and%20websites.%20And%20unless%20you%20plan%20on%20really%20pushing%20your%20computer%20to%20the%20limits%2C%20you%20don't%20need%2032GB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20upgrade%20laptops%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20depends%20on%20the%20laptop.%20Most%20Windows%20laptops%20will%20let%20you%20replace%20the%20battery%2C%20which%20is%20often%20the%20first%20piece%20of%20hardware%20to%20stop%20working.%20Some%20let%20you%20switch%20out%20the%20RAM%2C%20which%20is%20useful%20if%20you%20want%20to%20add%20more.%20Anything%20that's%20not%20soldered%20in%20can%20likely%20be%20replaced%2C%20but%20you%20should%20check%20with%20your%20laptop's%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacBooks%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20pretty%20set%20in%20stone.%20Even%20the%20batteries%20are%20held%20in%20place%20by%20glue%2C%20which%20is%20messy%20to%20dissolve.%20You'll%20probably%20want%20to%20leave%20any%20repairs%20to%20a%20professional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20tips%20on%20lengthening%20a%20laptop's%20lifespan%2C%20check%20out%20our%20article%20detailing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-long-do-laptops-last%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20long%20laptops%20last%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20operating%20system%20should%20I%20use%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20college%20laptops%20typically%20have%20one%20of%20three%20major%20operating%20systems%3A%20Windows%2C%20macOS%2C%20or%20ChromeOS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWindows%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20the%20most%20common%20and%20versatile%20operating%20system.%20Dozens%20of%20different%20companies%20produce%20Windows%20laptops%2C%20and%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20programs%20have%20a%20Windows%20version.%20Compared%20to%20macOS%20and%20ChromeOS%2C%20Windows%20is%20nearly%20infinitely%20customizable.%20It's%20the%20operating%20system%20I%20recommend%20for%20most%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMacOS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0is%20exclusive%20to%20(shocker)%20Apple%20computers.%20It's%20sleeker%20and%20easier%20to%20navigate%20than%20Windows%2C%20but%20it%20can't%20be%20customized%20as%20easily%20and%20has%20a%20smaller%20app%20library.%20MacBooks%20tend%20to%20have%20weaker%20graphical%20performance%20than%20PCs%2C%20too.%20If%20you're%20not%20a%20dedicated%20gamer%2C%20however%2C%20it's%20a%20fine%20alternative%20to%20Windows%2C%20and%20many%20people%20prefer%20its%20interface.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChromeOS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20designed%20by%20Google%2C%20and%20it's%20what%20you'll%20find%20on%20Chromebooks.%20Chromebook%20laptops%20are%20among%20the%20most%20affordable%20on%20the%20market%2C%20but%20in%20exchange%2C%20you%20get%20an%20operating%20system%20that%20actively%20restricts%20customization%20and%20features%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20supported%20programs.%20I%20wouldn't%20recommend%20ChromeOS%20to%20anyone%20but%20the%20most%20casual%20users.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuick%20tip%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20ChromeOS%20is%20actually%20built%20on%20top%20of%20a%20different%20operating%20system%20called%20%3Cstrong%3ELinux%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20isn't%20as%20well-known%20as%20other%20systems%20but%20has%20an%20incredibly%20passionate%20userbase.%20Most%20versions%20of%20Linux%20(called%20%26quot%3Bdistributions%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bdistros%26quot%3B)%20are%20free%20to%20install%2C%20and%20their%20minimalist%20nature%20makes%20them%20great%20for%20budget%20or%20old%20laptops.%20If%20you're%20really%20into%20coding%2C%20want%20an%20OS%20with%20less%20bloat%2C%20or%20want%20to%20support%20open%20source%20software%2C%20look%20into%20installing%20a%20distro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20some%20laptops%20better%20for%20certain%20college%20majors%20than%20others%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20guide%2C%20I've%20tried%20to%20pick%20the%20best%20college%20laptops%20that%20can%20suit%20the%20widest%20variety%20of%20majors%20without%20sacrificing%20portability.%20However%2C%20different%20classes%20have%20different%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20in%20the%20Humanities%20field%2C%20you%20won't%20need%20much%20from%20your%20laptop%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20enough%20CPU%20and%20RAM%20to%20handle%20dozens%20of%20browser%20tabs.%20But%20STEM%20majors%2C%20who%20often%20use%20complex%20physics%20and%20math%20modeling%20programs%2C%20will%20need%20a%20higher-end%20machine%2C%20like%20the%20Asus%20G14%2C%20with%20a%20powerful%20CPU%20and%20GPU.%20The%20same%20goes%20for%20artists%20and%20designers%2C%20especially%20if%20they're%20working%20with%20animation%20or%203D%20modeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20refurbished%20laptop%20models%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20depends%20on%20where%20you%20buy%20the%20refurbished%20laptop.%20I%20don't%20recommend%20refurbished%20laptops%20sold%20by%20third-party%20sellers%20on%20Amazon%2C%20Newegg%2C%20or%20other%20retailers%2C%20as%20there's%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20getting%20a%20unit%20with%20defects%20and%20other%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C