d%20clothes%2C%20despite%20my%20efforts%20to%20convince%20her%20that%20treasures%20could%20be%20found%20in%20other%20people's%20closets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthrift-shopping-mistakes-tips-for-buying-secondhand-clothes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESecondhand%20clothes%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20a%20normal%20part%20of%20my%20childhood%20in%20the%2080s%20and%2090s.%20I%20loved%20getting%20a%20box%20of%20%26quot%3Bhand-me-downs%26quot%3B%20because%20that%20was%20the%20only%20way%20for%20me%20to%20own%20clothes%20from%20the%20mall%20stores%20I%20wished%20my%20mom%20could%20take%20me%20to.%20Some%20of%20my%20favorite%20clothing%20items%20from%20my%20youth%20first%20belonged%20to%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20discovered%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclassic-thrift-stores-worse-secondhand-clothing-market-popular-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20is%20actually%20into%20thrifting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20thrilled.%20Still%2C%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20let%20my%20daughter%20buy%20things%20without%20seeing%20them%20in%20person.%20The%20popularity%20of%20fast%20fashion%20means%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20clothes%20being%20resold%20could%20be%20less%20than%20great.%20And%20then%20there's%20the%20issue%20of%20fit%3A%20sizing%20can%20be%20wildly%20different%20from%20brand%20to%20brand.%20Buying%20something%20with%20only%20a%20bad%20internet%20photo%20to%20guide%20you%20isn't%20the%20best%20practice%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20an%20inexperienced%20shopper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22277d6621-d77c-4a24-b296-18747580a85b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBy%20visiting%20a%20resale%20shop%20in%20person%2C%20I%20could%20teach%20her%20what%20was%20a%20good%20purchase%20and%20what%20was%20not%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20discovered%20a%20clothing%20resale%20store%20in%20our%20area%20that%20targets%20younger%20people.%20The%20store%20only%20sells%20clothing%20and%20accessories%2C%20so%20it%20felt%20more%20like%20a%20familiar%20shopping%20experience%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20looked%20at%20prices%20and%20brand%20tags%20and%20decided%20against%20buying%20anything%20we%20could%20get%20right%20now%20for%20the%20same%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-store-visits-why-company-struggling-images-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprice%20at%20Target%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Walmart.%20She%20found%20a%20couple%20of%20name-brand%20tops%20that%20would%20normally%20be%20out%20of%20our%20price%20range%2C%20but%20the%20real%20winner%20for%20us%20both%20was%20jeans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20daughter%20trying%20on%20clothes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a793cdcfc04e97619bd208%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20daughter%20trying%20on%20clothes.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20denim%20is%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20shop%20for%20at%20a%20resale%20shop%20because%20it%20is%20so%20expensive.%20She%20was%20able%20to%20find%20a%20pair%20of%20jeans%20in%20a%20cut%20she%20wanted%20that%20the%20stores%20in%20the%20mall%20don't%20sell%20right%20now.%20I%20even%20found%20jeans%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20find%20a%20pair%20of%20Levi's%20501s%20in%20my%20size%2C%20similar%20to%20a%20pair%20I%20used%20to%20own.%20More%20importantly%2C%20she%20%26quot%3Bapproved%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20jeans%2C%20which%20made%20the%20whole%20experience%20more%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee223d48-d7cc-401b-aec5-5ca75c52e732%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20paid%20for%206%20items%20at%20the%20resale%20shop%2C%20compared%20to%202%20at%20the%20mall%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20resale%20outing%20was%20definitely%20a%20success.%20I%20was%20proud%20of%20my%20daughter's%20choices%2C%20and%20she%20was%20so%20impressed%20with%20the%20savings%20that%20she%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20go%20back.%20So%20we%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20we%20returned%20to%20the%20same%20store%2C%20but%20this%20time%20we%20took%20advantage%20of%20their%20offer%20to%20buy%20used%20clothes.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20the%20amount%20they%20paid%20us%20for%20our%20clothes%20was%20greater%20than%20the%20price%20of%20the%20clothes%20we'd%20picked%20out%20to%20purchase.%20Which%20meant%20we%20spent%20nothing%2C%20and%20clothes%20that%20were%20taking%20up%20space%20in%20our%20house%20have%20a%20new%20home.%20Honestly%2C%20that%20just%20felt%20like%20a%20bonus%20since%20one%20of%20our%20finds%20included%20a%20dress%20that%20would%20have%20cost%20five%20times%20the%20price%20listed%20on%20the%20tag%20had%20we%20bought%20it%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20thrifting%20is%20definitely%20a%20trend%20for%20Gen%20Z%20right%20now%2C%20I%20prefer%20to%20present%20it%20to%20my%20daughter%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20use%20in%20the%20future.%20When%20fashion%20changes%20and%20the%20new%20styles%20aren't%20the%20right%20fit%2C%20it%20will%20be%20helpful%20for%20her%20to%20know%20how%20to%20find%20the%20clothes%20she%20wants.%20She%20will%20soon%20have%20her%20own%20money%20to%20spend%2C%20so%20I%20want%20to%20help%20her%20become%20a%20smarter%20shopper%20now%20instead%20of%20her%20learning%20the%20hard%20way%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20might%20not%20know%20everything%20about%20what%20Gen%20Z%20likes%20these%20days%2C%20but%20I%20know%20pinching%20your%20pennies%20never%20goes%20out%20of%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-took-my-teenager-thrifting-and-we-both-had-fun-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756500362000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a78441194a2d49b8aef7a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2