0water-resistant%20polyester%2FPVC%20material%20that%20completely%20resists%20odors%20and%20dampness%20and%20is%20well-suited%20for%20dogs%20who%20like%20to%20roll%20in%20the%20mud%20and%20romp%20on%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collar%20also%20has%20a%20band%20of%20reflective%20material%20visible%20in%20headlights%20up%20to%20150%20feet%2C%20which%20is%20useful%20for%20predawn%20or%20evening%20outings%20with%20your%20dog.%20Because%20BioThane%20is%20stiffer%20than%20nylon%20and%20leather%2C%20this%20collar%20is%20more%20difficult%20to%20adjust.%20Using%20the%20rings%20to%20thread%20the%20collar%20to%20the%20right%20size%20takes%20some%20effort%2C%20but%20once%20in%20place%2C%20the%20collar%20lies%20flat%20on%20the%20dog's%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20showing%20a%20wet%20dog%20wearing%20a%20neon%20green%20Stunt%20Puppy%20collar%20and%20a%20close-up%20of%20a%20yellow%20collar%20laid%20flat%20in%20a%20triangular%20shape.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b2086da17a8c5b4053c91e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20collar%20made%20of%20a%20tough%20blend%20of%20polyestery%20and%20PVC%20is%20an%20excellent%20choice%20for%20water-loving%20dogs.%3Cp%3EStunt%20Puppy%3B%20Amy%20Graves%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20collars%20we%20tested%2C%20its%20stiffness%20and%20thinness%20make%20it%20less%20comfortable%20for%20all-day%20wear%2C%20as%20it%20may%20dig%20into%20a%20dog's%20neck.%20You%20will%20want%20to%20take%20the%20collar%20off%20your%20dog%20when%20you%20get%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3642bce-7dc2-43b5-84fc-b3b32a07275e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20reflective%5C%22%3EBest%20reflective%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20was%20this%20personalizable%20L.L.Bean%20collar%20the%20most%20reflective%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20collars%2C%20but%20it%20was%20also%20durable%20and%20easily%20adjustable.%20The%20collar%20was%20visible%20in%20headlights%20from%20150%20feet%20away%20at%20night%2C%20so%20nighttime%20walks%20or%20predawn%20runs%20with%20your%20dog%20will%20feel%20much%20safer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20drawback%20is%20a%20rough%20edge%20to%20the%20stitching%20inside%20the%20collar.%20Because%20it%20feels%20scratchy%2C%20it%20won't%20work%20for%20all-day%20wear%20on%20short-haired%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20showing%20a%20dog%20wearing%20a%20gray%20reflective%20collar%20embroidered%20with%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BDusty%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20close-up%20of%20a%20similar%20collar%20embroidered%20with%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BScout%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20phone%20number.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b20975cfc04e97619c5516%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELL.Bean%20makes%20the%20most%20reflective%20collar%20we%20tested%2C%20and%20bonus%3A%20You%20can%20add%20embroidered%20text%20to%20personalize%20it.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Graves%3B%20L.L.Bean%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20personalization%2C%20the%20collar%20can%20fit%20up%20to%2023%20letters%20or%20numbers%20for%20the%20smallest%20size%20and%20up%20to%2030%20for%20the%20largest%2C%20stitched%20onto%20the%20material%20with%20black%20thread.%20Scotchlite%2C%20the%20collar's%20reflective%20material%2C%20is%20also%20used%20for%20safety%2C%20athletic%2C%20and%20casual%20garments.%20It%20is%20heat-bonded%20onto%20the%20fabric%20and%20did%20not%20fade%20or%20deteriorate%20in%20any%20of%20our%20rounds%20of%20soaking%20and%20machine%20washing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2287b2aa24-4cc1-451b-8e48-31edb3659025%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20LED%5C%22%3EBest%20LED%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Blazin%20LED%20Collar%20has%20three%20light-up%20modes%20(solid%2C%20blinking%2C%20and%20strobe)%20and%20keeps%20your%20dog%20visible%20during%20nighttime%20walks%20from%20at%20least%20150%20yards%20away.%20In%20solid%20mode%2C%20it%20stayed%20lit%20for%20just%20over%20four%20hours.%20It%20also%20proved%20durable%2C%20staying%20lit%20even%20when%20sprayed%20with%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20USB%20charging%20box%20built%20neatly%20into%20the%20end%2C%20the%20Blazin%20collar%20was%20a%20seamless%2C%20comfy%20fit%20on%20our%20test%20dog.%20The%20box%20closed%20securely%20after%20charging%2C%20so%20it%20resisted%20water%20well%20and%20kept%20working%20after%20we%20sprayed%20it%20with%20water%20to%20clean%20it%20up.%20Best%20of%20all%2C%20the%20collar%20lit%20up%20our%20test%20dog%20like%20a%20Christmas%20tree%20with%20a%20light%20bright%20enough%20for%20us%20to%20see%20her%20and%20for%20her%20to%20see%20what%20was%20in%20front%20of%20her.%20The%20LED%20lights%20take%20two%20hours%20to%20charge%20fully.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20showing%20two%20dogs%20wearing%20glowing%20green%20LED%20collars%2C%20one%20indoors%20and%20one%20outside%20at%20dusk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b209efcfc04e97619c5529%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Blazin'%20LED%20collar%20shines%20bright%2C%20even%20on%20long-haired%20dogs.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Graves%3B%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20side-release%20plastic%20buckle%20was%20easy%20to%20open%20and%20close%2C%20and%20the%20nylon%20collar%20was%20easy%20to%20adjust%20for%20size%2C%20even%20with%20the%20built-in%20strip%20of%20LED%20lights.%20Inside%2C%20it%20was%20smooth%20on%20the%20dog's%20neck.%20The%20is%20available%20in%20a%20range%20of%20colors%2C%20but%20we%20found%20one%20clear%20advantage%20to%20the%20neon%20green%20model%20we%20tested%3A%20It%20stood%20out%20clearly%20on%20our%20dog%20at%2050%20feet%20away%20in%20semi-darkness%2C%20even%20with%20the%20LED%20lights%20turned%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a999ae76-b305-49e8-b222-b008aaf94ed1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20comfort%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20comfort%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20dogs%20with%20short%20hair%2C%20sensitive%20skin%2C%20or%20an%20aversion%20to%20equipment%2C%20this%20collar%20is%20our%20top%20pick.%20It%20features%20a%20combination%20of%20thick%20padding%20and%20breathable%20mesh%2C%20making%20it%20a%20good%20option%20for%20choosy%20dogs%2C%20like%20our%20tester%20pup%20%E2%80%94%20a%2026-pound%20mini%20pinscher%20mix%20who%20typically%20dislikes%20wearing%20gear.%20She%20took%20to%20this%20collar%20with%20no%20complaints.%20This%20came%20as%20little%20surprise%2C%20since%20Chai's%20Choice%20is%20the%20brand%20she%20finally%20tolerated%20after%20a%20lengthy%20search%20for%20the%20most%20comfortable%20dog%20harness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20collar%20doesn't%20have%20any%20scratchy%20stitching%20that%20can%20irritate%20the%20skin%2C%20and%20the%20buckle%20sits%20on%20top%20of%20the%20mesh%20layer%2C%20so%20it%20doesn't%20touch%20your%20dog's%20neck.%20It's%20also%20soft%20and%20flexible.%20Although%20it's%20a%20little%20heavier%20than%20other%20collars%20we've%20tested%2C%20it%20still%20feels%20lightweight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20showing%20a%20brown%20dog%20wearing%20a%20black-and-yellow%20reflective%20collar%20and%20a%20close-up%20of%20the%20same%20collar%20displayed%20on%20a%20white%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b20ace194a2d49b8af7c14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWith%20substantial%20padding%20and%20breathable%20mesh%2C%20the%20Chai's%20Choice%20Comfort%20Collar%20may%20be%20a%20good%20option%20for%20dogs%20that%20are%20reluctant%20to%20wear%20a%20collar.%3Cp%3ELiz%20Coleman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20collar%20is%20sturdy%20and%20well-constructed%2C%20it%20can%20be%20awkward%20to%20put%20on%20and%20adjust%20the%20size.%20You%20have%20to%20pass%20the%20buckle%20through%20the%20metal%20O-ring%2C%20which%20can%20be%20tricky%20with%20a%20resistant%20dog.%20But%20if%20comfort%20is%20your%20priority%2C%20we%20don't%20consider%20this%20a%20dealbreaker.%20Just%20remember%20to%20check%20the%20sizing%20closely%20since%20the%20collar%20can%20only%20be%20adjusted%20a%20couple%20of%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220119f56c-6e8a-49e7-9a7e-0800ed4c7bf9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Frisco%20Nylon%20Collar%20is%20a%20great%20all-around%20budget%20choice%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dog%20collars.%20Both%20durable%20and%20pliable%2C%20it%20held%20up%20in%20all%20kinds%20of%20abuse%20tests%2C%20showing%20no%20%26quot%3Bteeth%26quot%3B%20marks%20from%20pounding%20with%20a%20meat%20mallet%20or%20hardware%20damage%20or%20decay%20from%20prolonged%20soaking%20or%20pulling.%20Its%20only%20drawbacks%20are%20its%20limited%20range%20of%20colors%20and%20the%20choice%20of%20only%20%C2%BE-inch%20width%20for%20the%20medium%20size%20collar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMade%20of%20tough%20but%20pliable%20nylon%20with%207%20inches%20of%20adjustability%2C%20the%20Frisco%20collar%20is%20hard%20to%20beat.%20Its%20D-ring%20stayed%20strong%20and%20did%20not%20discolor%20with%20prolonged%20wetness%2C%20and%20the%20fabric%20uses%20UltraWeld%2C%20a%20silicone%20fabric%20sealant%20that%20is%20highly%20resistant%20to%20tearing%20and%20chew%20marks.%20As%20for%20ease%20of%20use%2C%20Frisco%20has%20you%20covered%20with%20an%20easy-to-manipulate%20side-release%20buckle%20and%20a%20nickel-coated%20aluminum%20D-ring%20that%20doesn't%20impede%20tag%20attachment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20showing%20a%20black%20poodle%20wearing%20a%20plain%20red%20Frisco%20collar%20and%20a%20close-up%20of%20the%20same%20collar%20laid%20flat%20on%20a%20white%20surface.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b20b1ccfc04e97619c5556%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Frisco%20Nylon%20Dog%20Collar%20nails%20the%20basics%2C%20providing%20excellent%20value%20for%20under%20%2410.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Graves%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20downside%3A%20At%20%C2%BE-inch%20wide%2C%20the%20size%20medium%20collar%20won't%20accommodate%20all%20medium-sized%20dogs.%20It%20fits%20dogs%20with%20necks%20from%2014%20to%2020%20inches%20in%20circumference%20but%20looks%20a%20bit%20skimpy%20on%20the%20neck%20of%20a%20standard%20poodle%20and%20is%20completely%20unsuitable%20for%20the%20larger%20neck%20and%20smaller%20head%20of%20a%20greyhound%20or%20Afghan%20hound%2C%20for%20instance.%20The%20next%20size%20up%2C%20for%2018-%20to%2026-inch%20neck%20circumferences%2C%20comes%20in%20a%201-inch%20width.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225db9254e-6718-4835-8db8-5b1d1c81cbb1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20collar%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Twelve%20different%20dog%20collars%20in%20various%20colors%20laid%20out%20on%20a%20white%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3e1e4048ff200190ce065%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeven%20of%20the%20twelve%20collars%20we%20tested%20rose%20to%20the%20top%2C%20thanks%20to%20some%20key%20features.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Graves%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20consulted%20several%20veterinarians%20to%20determine%20which%20features%20are%20most%20important%20to%20focus%20on.%20Rather%20than%20choosing%20a%20collar%20based%20solely%20on%20aesthetics%20or%20style%2C%20consider%20the%20following%20factors%20to%20ensure%20your%20dog's%20comfort%20and%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecure%20closure%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECollars%20have%20two%20types%20of%20closures%3A%20plastic%20side-release%20tabs%20and%20metal%20belt-buckle%20types.%20For%20ease%20of%20use%2C%20the%20side-release%20tabs%20work%20best%20since%20they%20can%20be%20released%20with%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20all%20the%20models%20we%20tested%20held%20up%20securely%20in%20all%20our%20tests.%20Side-release%20tabs%20that%20open%20the%20collar%20quickly%20can%20help%20if%20your%20dog%20gets%20caught%20on%20something%20while%20wearing%20their%20collar%2C%20Collins%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20metal%20buckles%2C%20common%20on%20leather%20collars%2C%20did%20not%20fail%20us%20either.%20But%20they%20have%20ease%20of%20use%20issues%20since%20they%20can%20only%20be%20secured%20at%20notches%20on%20the%20collar%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20to%20get%20the%20perfect%20fit%20on%20the%20dog's%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHardware%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20collar%20is%20for%20carrying%20your%20dog's%20ID%20tags%2C%20so%20it%20should%20have%20a%20solid%20D-%20or%20V-shaped%20ring%20made%20from%20a%20durable%20metal%20like%20stainless%20steel%20or%20aluminum%20for%20attaching%20the%20tags.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20such%20a%20thing%20as%20too%20solid%3A%20A%20collar%20with%20an%20extra%20thick%2C%20bulky%20ring%20can%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20work%20with.%20Anyone%20who%20has%20struggled%20to%20thread%20the%20wire%20loop%20that%20holds%20the%20tags%20to%20the%20D-ring%20knows%20firsthand%20that%20prying%20the%20wire%20apart%20to%20attach%20it%20to%20a%20thick%20ring%20is%20too%20much%20work%2C%20if%20not%20impossible.%20Some%20collars%20have%20two%20rings%20%E2%80%94%20one%20for%20ID%20tags%20and%20one%20for%20attaching%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-leash%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20leashes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20we%20do%20not%20recommend%20using%20any%20collar%20for%20leash%20walking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdjustability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGetting%20the%20right%20fit%20on%20your%20dog's%20neck%20is%20essential%20for%20collar%20comfort%20and%20safety.%20Even%20the%20proper%20size%20collar%20needs%20fine-tuning%2C%20and%20we%20found%20those%20that%20offer%20at%20least%204%20inches%20of%20adjustability%20are%20the%20easiest%20to%20fit%20to%20a%20dog.%20On%20fabric%20collars%2C%20size%20adjustment%20means%20threading%20the%20collars%20through%20tabs%20that%20allow%20you%20to%20double%20it%20up%2C%20thus%20sizing%20the%20collar%20down.%20Stiffer%2C%20bulkier%20materials%20can%20be%20more%20difficult%20to%20adjust.%20On%20leather%20collars%2C%20all%20you%20have%20to%20work%20with%20is%20the%20belt%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFor%20overall%20comfort%2C%20look%20for%20a%20collar%20that%20is%20smooth%20on%20the%20inside%20where%20it%20touches%20the%20neck.%20Any%20stray%20stitches%20or%20material%20sticking%20out%20may%20irritate%20short-haired%20dogs.%20Pliability%20is%20also%20important%20since%20a%20stiff%20collar%20could%20dig%20into%20a%20dog's%20neck%20if%20caught%20on%20anything.%20As%20for%20overall%20collar%20weight%2C%20less%20is%20more.%20%26quot%3BThe%20collar%20should%20not%20sag%2C%20which%20would%20suggest%20it's%20either%20too%20big%20or%20too%20heavy%20for%20the%20dog%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kingsdale.com%2Fvet-clinic-kitchener%2Fteam%2Fvets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Brad%20Hinsperger%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20director%20of%20Kingsdale%20Animal%20Hospital%20in%20Kitchener%2C%20Ontario%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collar's%20width%20is%20important%2C%20too.%20Hinsperger%20says%20dogs%20with%20long%20necks%20and%20small%20heads%2C%20like%20greyhounds%2C%20do%20best%20with%20a%20wider%20collar%20(1.5%20to%202%20inches)%2C%20which%20minimizes%20friction%20on%20their%20delicate%20skin.%20For%20smaller%20dogs%2C%20like%20Shih%20Tzus%20and%20Yorkies%2C%20a%20narrower%20collar%20is%20ideal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Woven%20nylon%20and%20BioThane%20collars%20are%20more%20durable%20and%20easier%20to%20clean%20than%20other%20materials%2C%20and%20most%20can%20go%20through%20the%20washing%20machine.%20Leather%20collars%20are%20not%20washing-machine-safe%20since%20prolonged%20wetness%20will%20waterlog%20them%20and%20eventually%20dry%20them%20out%20to%20brittle%20pretzels%20(which%20we%20know%20from%20once%20trying%20to%20wash%20a%20leather%20leash).%20Hand%20washing%20in%20warm%2C%20soapy%20water%20is%20your%20only%20option%20for%20leather.%20For%20dogs%20with%20sensitive%20skin%20or%20dermatitis%2C%20it%20helps%20to%20avoid%20rough%20or%20stiff%20materials.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20recommend%20a%20good%20quality%20nylon%20collar%20in%20these%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Hinsperger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237cbfdba-838c-4278-83c5-84ea109d3d6d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20dog%20collars%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20different%20dog%20collars%20are%20hanging%20from%20ceiling%20beams%20with%20bricks%20attached.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3e295048ff200190ce294%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20best%20dog%20collars%20we%20tested%20were%20subjected%20to%20a%20fabric%20durability%20test.%3Cp%3EAmy%20Graves%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20the%20best%20dog%20collars%2C%20we%20tested%20them%20on%20three%20different%20dogs%3A%20an%20Australian%20shepherd%20with%20long%20hair%2C%20a%20standard%20poodle%2C%20and%20a%20short-haired%20miniature%20pinscher%20mix.%20We%20pulled%2C%20pounded%2C%20and%20poked%2016%20collars%2C%20adjusted%20and%20readjusted%20their%20sizing%2C%20attached%20and%20removed%20ID%20tags%2C%20buried%20them%20in%20the%20dirt%2C%20soaked%20them%20in%20vinegar%2C%20and%20weighted%20them%20down%20with%20bricks%20to%20stress%20the%20fabric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHardware%20durability%20and%20performance%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20make%20sure%20they%20were%20durable%20and%20long-lasting%2C%20we%20put%20the%20D-rings%20and%20closures%20through%20some%20tough%20testing.%20We%20attached%20the%20collars%20to%20leashes%20and%20closed%20them%20around%20a%20fixed%2C%20solid%20support%20beam.%20With%20the%20Chai's%20Choice%20collar%2C%20we%20had%20a%20partner%20hold%20the%20collar%20securely%20in%20place.%20Then%2C%20we%20yanked%2C%20pulled%2C%20and%20twisted%20them%20to%20find%20any%20weak%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFabric%20durability%20and%20performance%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20soiling%20the%20collars%20with%20dirt%20and%20letting%20them%20sit%20overnight%2C%20we%20made%20cuts%20in%20them%20with%20scissors%20or%20a%20paring%20knife%20and%20tied%20them%20to%204-pound%20bricks%20to%20weigh%20them%20down%20for%2024%20hours.%20Then%2C%20we%20checked%20back%20in%20to%20see%20if%20the%20cuts%20grew%20larger.%20For%20some%20collars%2C%20including%20Chai's%20Choice%2C%20we%20instead%20pulled%20both%20ends%20of%20the%20collar%20after%20attempting%20to%20make%20cuts%20to%20see%20if%20the%20fabric%20would%20tear%20further.%20We%20also%20pounded%20each%20collar%20with%20a%20meat%20mallet%20to%20simulate%20dog%20chew%20marks%20and%20examined%20both%20the%20fabric%20and%20the%20hardware%2C%20looking%20for%20discoloration%20and%20signs%20of%20corrosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPet%20comfort%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESince%20dogs%20cannot%20always%20communicate%20their%20sartorial%20preferences%2C%20we%20put%20each%20of%20the%20collars%20around%20not%20only%20dogs'%20necks%20but%20also%20our%20own%2C%20looking%20for%20scratchy%20stitching%20and%20irritating%20material%20stiffness.%20With%20dogs%20wearing%20the%20collars%2C%20we%20looked%20for%20proper%20neck%20movement%20and%20whether%20the%20collar%20could%20lie%20flat%20on%20the%20neck.%20We%20deducted%20points%20for%20excessive%20shaking%2C%20scratching%2C%20or%20head%20wagging%20that%20might%20indicate%20irritation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAdjusting%20a%20collar's%20size%20and%20getting%20tags%20in%20place%20easily%20saves%20time%20and%20effort%2C%20so%20we%20put%20all%20the%20collars%20to%20these%20tests%20and%20deducted%20points%20for%20anything%20bulky%2C%20such%20as%20too-thick%20rings%20that%20had%20us%20prying%20away%20to%20loop%20tags%20on%20or%20stubborn%20buckles%20and%20stiff%20collar%20fabrics%20that%20stuck%20when%20threading%20them.%20As%20for%20putting%20the%20collar%20on%20and%20taking%20it%20off%2C%20the%20side-release%20closures%20on%20all%20but%20the%20leather%20models%20should%20be%20easy%20to%20open%20one-handed%3B%20we%20took%20off%20points%20for%20those%20that%20took%20more%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpray%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20simulate%20dog%20walks%20in%20the%20rain%2C%20we%20sprayed%20all%20the%20collars%20with%20the%20spray%20nozzle%20at%20our%20kitchen%20sink%20%E2%80%94%20even%20the%20LED%20models%2C%20which%20continued%20to%20function%20normally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleaning%20test%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20soaked%20all%20the%20collars%20in%20vinegar%20for%2030%20minutes%20to%20make%20them%20very%20stinky.%20Then%2C%20we%20tested%20smell%20retention%20by%20cleaning%20them%20to%20see%20if%20odors%20stuck%20around.%20Except%20for%20the%20LED%20collars%2C%20which%20we%20hand-washed%20in%20hot%2C%20soapy%20water%2C%20we%20used%20the%20regular%20cycle%20on%20our%20washing%20machine.%20While%20the%20collars%20that%20got%20this%20treatment%20all%20came%20out%20looking%20clean%20and%20no%20longer%20smelling%20of%20vinegar%2C%20a%20few%20showed%20corrosion%20and%20rust%20on%20the%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturn%20policy%20and%20warranty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECollars%20with%20generous%20refund%20policies%20got%20high%20marks.%20Those%20available%20on%20Chewy%20are%20covered%20by%20the%20retailer's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110344588fm-20%26h%3Da28cf3e185daa88943fa5dfafa9fe4450ace90c32cd2932559661dff0a3c7474%26postID%3D68b1e18cd98ccb140cc2bf6c%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fpets-best-dog-collars%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fapp%252Fcontent%252Ffaq%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E365-day%20guarantee%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Others%20offered%20full%20refunds%20for%20factory%20defects%2C%20which%20was%20less%20valuable%20in%20our%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAvailable%20colors%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESince%20personal%20preferences%20and%20dog%20fur%20colors%20vary%2C%20we%20looked%20for%20collars%20that%20came%20in%20a%20range%20of%20options.%20Some%20of%20our%20top%20picks%20have%20limited%20color%20choices%2C%20but%20their%20other%20attributes%20won%20us%20over.%20We'd%20rather%20have%20a%20collar%20that's%20easy%2C%20safe%20to%20use%2C%20and%20stands%20the%20test%20of%20time%2C%20even%20if%20the%20color%20it%20came%20in%20wasn't%20our%20first%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac906413-6d88-4a4c-9581-78354f55d073%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EDog%20collars%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20collar%20for%20a%20dog%20to%20wear%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20type%20of%20collar%20depends%20on%20the%20specific%20dog%20to%20some%20extent.%20While%20all%20dogs%20do%20best%20with%20a%20collar%20that%20will%20lie%20flat%20on%20the%20neck%2C%20close%20securely%2C%20and%20provide%20a%20place%20to%20attach%20ID%20tags%2C%20thinner%20bands%20(%C2%BD%20to%20%C2%BE%20inches)%20are%20better%20for%20toy%20breeds%20and%20other%20small%20dogs%2C%20while%20thick%20collars%20(1%20to%201%20%C2%BD%20inches)%20work%20for%20larger%20breeds.%20For%20dogs%20with%20larger%20necks%20and%20smaller%20heads%2C%20a%20martingale-style%20collar%20will%20be%20best%2C%20adds%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abwellnesscenter.com%2Fteam%2F-------amy-l.-pike%2C-dvm%2C-dacvb%2C-iaabc-cdbc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Amy%20L.%20Pike%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinary%20behaviorist%20and%20owner%20of%20Animal%20Behavior%20Wellness%20Center.%20This%20design%20keeps%20the%20collar%20from%20slipping%20over%20the%20dog's%20head%20when%20a%20leash%20is%20attached.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20best%20dog%20collar%20for%20any%20pup%20is%20one%20that%20fits%20well%20and%20is%20comfortable%20enough%20to%20leave%20on%20for%20long%20stretches%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20vets%20recommend%20collars%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECollars%20are%20recommended%20whenever%20a%20dog%20is%20outside%20so%20someone%20can%20easily%20identify%20the%20dog%20and%20in%20case%20you%20need%20to%20grab%20hold%20of%20it%20to%20separate%20your%20dog%20from%20another%20dog%20safely.%20Collins%20says%20a%20collar%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20backup%20if%20your%20dog's%20harness%20gives%20way.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20gear%20to%20safely%20and%20comfortably%20walk%20your%20dog%2C%20we%20recommend%20outfitting%20your%20pup%20with%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-harness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20harnesses%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-no-pull-dog-harness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20no-pull%20dog%20harnesses%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20attaching%20their%20leash%20directly%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20safest%20collar%20for%20dogs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECollins%20says%20the%20safest%20collar%20should%20be%20adjustable%20to%20fit%20the%20dog's%20neck%20with%20room%20left%20over%2C%20be%20easy%20to%20remove%2C%20and%20carry%20a%20dog's%20identification%20tags%20securely.%20Also%2C%20consider%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20collar%3A%20You%20don't%20want%20to%20overburden%20a%20toy%20breed%20with%20hefty%20neckwear.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20dog%20holds%20their%20head%20in%20a%20lower%20position%20with%20a%20collar%20on%20versus%20the%20collar%20off%2C%20then%20it's%20too%20heavy%2C%26quot%3B%20Pike%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20should%20be%20able%20to%20easily%20lift%2C%20lower%2C%20and%20turn%20their%20head%20with%20the%20collar%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20a%20martingale%20collar%20good%20for%20dogs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMartingale%20collars%20are%20designed%20with%20an%20extra%20loop%20of%20fabric%20that%20tightens%20gently%20(but%20not%20too%20tightly)%20when%20pressure%20is%20applied.%20Hinsperger%20recommends%20them%20for%20most%20dogs.%20Martingale%20collars%20can%20be%20used%20for%20regular%2C%20everyday%20wear.%20When%20attached%20to%20a%20harness%20using%20a%20safety%20clip%2C%20martingale%20collars%20offer%20added%20security%20for%20dogs%20who%20tend%20to%20slip%20out%20of%20flat%20collars%20and%20harnesses.%20This%20is%20especially%20beneficial%20for%20breeds%20with%20long%20necks%20and%20small%20heads%2C%20such%20as%20greyhounds%20and%20Afghan%20hounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20a%20prong%20collar%20bad%20for%20dogs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20recommended%20to%20avoid%20using%20prong%20collars%20and%20other%20aversive%20tools.%20Pike%20says%20that%20prong%20collars%20can%20cause%20serious%20injuries%2C%20such%20as%20puncture%20wounds%2C%20and%20may%20increase%20fear%20and%20anxiety%20in%20dogs%20by%20punishing%20them%20for%20pulling.%20This%20can%20damage%20the%20trust%20between%20a%20dog%20and%20their%20owner%20and%20may%20lead%20to%20behavioral%20problems%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20dogs%20wear%20collars%20at%20home%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EVeterinarians%20agree%20that%20it%20is%20best%20to%20take%20collars%20off%20whenever%20dogs%20play%20with%20one%20another%20or%20are%20at%20home%20alone.%20%26quot%3BFor%20ultimate%20safety%2C%20it's%20best%20never%20to%20have%20a%20collar%20on%20a%20dog%20at%20home%2C%20unless%20you%20are%20with%20them%20the%20whole%20time%2C''%20Collins%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20point%20is%20it%20can%20get%20caught%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20furniture%2C%20on%20another%20dog's%20collar%2C%20or%20a%20dog%20could%20get%20its%20teeth%20on%20the%20collar%2C%20or%20they%20could%20get%20their%20foot%20through%20it%20if%20it's%20too%20loose.''%20Since%20so%20many%20things%20can%20go%20wrong%2C%20removing%20the%20collar%20makes%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20tightly%20should%20a%20collar%20be%20worn%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20misconception%20is%20that%20two%20fingers%20should%20fit%20between%20the%20dog's%20neck%20and%20collar%20when%20it%20should%20really%20be%20looser.%20%26quot%3BIt%20should%20be%20loose%20enough%20so%20that%20it%20lies%20flat%20and%20the%20dog%20is%20not%20bothered%20by%20it%2C''%20Collins%20says.%20As%20for%20positioning%20on%20the%20neck%2C%20aim%20lower%20than%20the%20dog's%20larynx%2C%20closer%20to%20the%20shoulders.%20Collins%20says%20this%20avoids%20a%20sensitive%20area%20of%20the%20neck%20that%20can%20be%20damaged%20with%20too%20much%20pressure.%20Finally%2C%20the%20thickness%20of%20a%20collar%20relative%20to%20the%20size%20of%20the%20neck%20is%20important.%20He%20says%20thinner%20collars%20are%20for%20small%20neck%20circumferences%20only.%20All%20of%20the%20collars%20we%20tested%20were%20either%20%C2%BE-%20or%201-inch%20thick%2C%20which%20worked%20on%20our%20medium-sized%20dog%2C%20but%20most%20of%20them%20were%20available%20in%20%C2%BD-inch%20thickness%20in%20smaller%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3