3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20need%20communities%20to%20be%20able%20to%20trust%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mawakana%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo's%20self-driving%20cars%20include%20a%20valuable%20resource%20for%20law%20enforcement%3A%20a%20bunch%20of%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20long%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawmakers-letter-amazon-ring-police-partnerships-terms-of-service-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esought%20data%20from%20tech%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20Amazon%20and%20others%2C%20during%20their%20investigations.%20Now%20they%20are%20doing%20the%20same%20for%20self-driving%20cars.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-lidar-sensor-versus-cameras-vision-only-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWaymo%20installs%2029%20cameras%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20each%20robotaxi%2C%20prompting%20some%20to%20question%20how%20much%20access%20authorities%20have%20to%20footage%20captured%20during%20rides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20interview%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BHard%20Fork%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20on%20Friday%2C%20Waymo%20co-CEO%20Tekedra%20Mawakana%20said%20the%20company%20adheres%20to%20a%20legal%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20question%20of%20when%20and%20how%20law%20enforcement%20gets%20access%20to%20our%20data%2C%20we%20make%20that%20publicly%20known%2C%26quot%3B%20Mawakana%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20follow%20the%20legal%20process%20to%20receive%20footage%20from%20our%20vehicles%2C%20and%20we%20narrow%20the%20scope%20of%20that%20as%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Waymo%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it%20requires%20law%20enforcement%20to%20make%20a%20%26quot%3Bvalid%26quot%3B%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20general%20matter%2C%20we%20require%20valid%20legal%20process%20(in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20warrant%20or%20court%20order)%20from%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20who%20s