%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIncreasing%20yields%20and%20boosting%20soil%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArduous%20laboratory%20hours%20and%20field%20tests%20resulted%20in%20a%20five-step%20processing%20technology%20that%20balanced%20toxic%20metals%20and%20enriched%20the%20slag%E2%80%99s%20natural%20resource%20components.%20Her%20formula%20enhanced%20nutrient%20absorption%20and%20microbial%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20innovation%20effectively%20controls%20the%20toxic%20metal%20content%20within%20the%20waste.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20components%20are%20formulated%20to%20boost%20microbial%20activity%20and%20neutralise%20acidic%20soil%E2%80%99s%20pH%20balance.%20This%20transformation%20not%20only%20addresses%20the%20environmental%20challenges%20posed%20by%20LD%20slag%20but%20also%20provides%20a%20sustainable%20solution%20for%20enhancing%20soil%20and%20plant%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dr%20Sahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-4-1755836386.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sahu's%20company%2C%20Biotez%20Agrinovation%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%2C%20produces%202%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20bio-fertiliser%20monthly.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-4-1755836386.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-4-1755836386-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-4-1755836386-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-4-1755836386-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fsteel-slag-fertiliser-4-1755836386-15